Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Fourth of July
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wvsy
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 4 Jul 1982
Changing ways of celebrating the Fourth of July. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.